'''小舌鼻音'''是[[輔音|輔音]]的一種，在[[國際音標|國際音標]]中以'''{{IPA|{{尖括号|ɴ}}}}'''（即小型大写字母N）表示，在[[X-SAMPA|X-SAMPA]]中以<code>N\</code>表示。因为響度高，且很難在小舌接觸時產生鼻腔發音，所以極為罕見。僅在少數幾種口語中作為音位出現。<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=A note on the Inuit uvular nasal|last=Johnson|first=Marion|date=1978|journal=Études/Inuit/Studies|issue=1|volume=2|pages=132–135}}</ref>
常以其他音素的變體出現，<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Bobaljik|first=Jonathan David|date=October 1996|title=Assimilation in the Inuit Languages and the Place of the Uvular Nasal|journal=International Journal of American Linguistics |volume=62 |issue=4 |pages=323–350|publisher=The University of Chicago Press|doi=10.1086/466303|jstor=1265705}}</ref> 例如在[[克丘亞語|克丘亞語]]中在[[小舌塞音|小舌塞音]]之前為/n/的音位變體，或在Selkup中在另一個鼻音前為/q/的音位變體。 但是，據報導它在少數幾種語言中作為獨立的音位存在。 例子包括[[克拉蘭語|克拉蘭語]]，[[圖阿雷格柏柏爾語|圖阿雷格柏柏爾語]]的Tawellemmet和Ayr變種<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Khams Tibetan Rangakha dialect: phonetic analysis (in Japanese)|url=http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/51094/1/aall002008.pdf|last=Suzuki|first=Hiroyuki|date=2007|journal=Asian and African Languages and Linguistics|issue=2|pages=131–162|access-date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002234836/http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/51094/1/aall002008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Khams藏族的Rangakha方言，<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Suzuki|first=Hiroyuki|date=2007|title=Khams Tibetan Rangakha dialect: phonetic analysis (in Japanese)|url=http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/51094/1/aall002008.pdf|journal=Asian and African Languages and Linguistics|issue=2|pages=131–162|access-date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002234836/http://repository.tufs.ac.jp/bitstream/10108/51094/1/aall002008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>至少兩種[[白語|白語]]<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|title=Bai Dialect Survey|last=Allen|first=Bryan|date=August 2007|work=SIL Electronic Survey Report 2007-012|citeseerx = 10.1.1.692.4221}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|last=Feng|first=Wang|date=2006|title=Comparison of Languages in Contact: The Distillation Method and the Case of Bai|url=http://www.ling.sinica.edu.tw/Files/LL/UploadFiles/MonoFullText/WF-Bai-All.pdf|journal=Language and Linguistics Monograph Series B. Frontiers in Linguistics III|access-date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2018-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180320230855/http://www.ling.sinica.edu.tw/Files/LL/UploadFiles/MonoFullText/WF-Bai-All.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，巴布亞語Mapos Buang。在Mapos Buang和白語中，它與[[软腭鼻音|软腭鼻音]]对立。

在Yanyuwa语等语言中存在'''前小舌鼻音'''(pre-uvular<ref>Instead of "pre-uvular", it can be called "advanced uvular", "fronted uvular", "post-velar", "retracted velar" or "backed velar". For simplicity, this article uses only the term "pre-uvular".</ref> nasal)，该音的发音位置比小舌鼻音靠前，介于软腭鼻音和小舌鼻音之间。它也是汉语[[普通话|普通话]]中[[后鼻音|后鼻音]]的[[音位变体|音位变体]]之一。用国际音标表记这个音需要添加附加符号，为{{IPA|[ɴ̟]}}, {{IPA|[ŋ̠]}}或{{IPA|[ŋ˗]}}。此音的X-SAMPA符号是<code>N\_+</code> 或<code>N_-</code>。

